      • useFileTileCache

        public javafx.beans.property.BooleanProperty useFileTileCacheProperty
        This BooleanProperty describes whether the FileTileCache is allowed to be used. If the value is set to false, every Tile is needs to be rendered before it can be displayed. Also it will be discarded if the MemoryTileCache is full
